			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "My ears are open for Hey Jibo, then once I hear those magic words, I listen to what you say next so I can respond to you. Also if I ask you a question or just say hello to you, you'll see my light ring and <phoneme ph='m ai ai'> myeye </phoneme> turn blue, that means I'm listening for your response. <break size='0.5'/>If you have more questions about your privacy, there is a lot of info on the jibo website, at jibo dot com slash privacy.",
			"media": "TTS",
			"prompt_id": "SUP_GEN_WhenListening_AN_01",
