			"prompt_sub_category": "AN",
			"index": 1,
			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "I listen for Hey Jibo, then once I hear those magic words, I respond to whatever you say next. And sometimes I'll ask <pitch mult='1.3'>you</pitch> a question, or say something you can respond to. You'll see my light ring and <phoneme ph='m ai ai'> myeye </phoneme> turn blue, to show you that I'm <pitch mult='1.2'>ready</pitch> to hear what you have to say. <break size='0.5'/>If you're wondering about your privacy, there's a lot of info on the jibo website, at jibo dot com slash privacy.",
